  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5142640/" class="title-link">噪音太多</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5142640"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/kanagawa/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1883644-22.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kanagawa/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">黑色镜框</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-10-25"
      class="main-meta">2011-10-25 11:10:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5142640_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         我怎么觉得这书被虚炒了啊。作者提到的抗议歌手人尽皆知，我还以为他发掘了什么不为人知的资源呢。况且文笔也不好，不喜欢这种在叙述中夹入大量议论、抒情的笔法——对我来说，太多的议论、抒情是种“噪音”。     比如讲迪伦那章，兜兜转转讲那么多，对迪伦为什么从关...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
